2. Recreate Strategy
All old pods are terminated at once before new pods are started.

1.❌ Downtime posRolling Update (Default Strategy)
This strategy updates pods gradually, ensuring that some pods remain available during the update process.

✔ No downtime ✔ Version overlap: New and old pods run together temporarily ✔ Ideal for production environmentssible ❌ 
All pods stopped before new ones start ✔ Simple, clean rollout ✔ Used in dev/testing environments where downtime is acceptable


